00:29:03.940 --> 00:29:08.740
And that's because one of the principles of
how we store the collection is that we try

00:29:08.740 --> 00:29:12.320
to make everything as reversible as possible.

00:29:12.320 --> 00:29:18.679
So we try whenever we do anything to a photograph
to allow it to be undone.

00:29:18.679 --> 00:29:20.850
We try not to hinge it whenever we can.

00:29:20.850 --> 00:29:24.010
We use photo corners instead.

00:29:24.010 --> 00:29:27.200
And so those are decisions that you can make
with your own photographs.

00:29:27.200 --> 00:29:31.710
Like if you put a lot of tape on the back
of your picture, if you ever have to remove

00:29:31.710 --> 00:29:33.659
that tape, you are gonna have problems.

00:29:33.659 --> 00:29:36.500
So keep that in mind.

